{"tid":59742,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何盡快忘記對你冇感覺的人","createTime":"2016-12-30T01:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T06:14:21.000Z","uid":19331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e8c5bea908a73495327c2d565a460c3effc1ef","tid":59742,"uid":19331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:38:28.000Z","msg":"大家a0 識左一個月 興趣相同<br />\nWhatsapp乜都吹<br />\n佢有主動聊講野<br />\n有試過講下曖昧野 佢冇反感<br />\nSnapchat黃心左幾個禮拜<br />\n佢成日諗野負面 我就開解佢<br />\n冇單獨出過街 但有同幾個fd 咁<br />\n有一日好夜返屋企 佢驚<br />\n打電話比我 同佢吹水吹到佢行返屋企<br />\n過幾日表白左<br />\n被fdzone<br />\n佢話冇feel<br />\n我話唔緊要 be fd 都ok<br />\n叫佢唔好太責怪自己<br />\n<br />\n而家食唔安訓唔落<br />\n希望盡快忘記佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日訓訓下隔一個鐘就醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論 毒撚切忌ff <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8375a67b6f313136c4ec611ffd04e6f46bacb8f","tid":59742,"uid":19331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8568ac06aa32d6d468ff06eed52cd4f6166ae640","tid":59742,"uid":54031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:45:24.000Z","msg":"毒撚切忌表白是常識"},{"pid":"e07d6a543c1a3e968d5017a5066976f8ba65b90b","tid":59742,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e053b90cb58912aaf4086da6c28911a8a24e6b4","tid":59742,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:34